videos.description: Florida State's Terance Mann pokes the ball loose and goes all the way for the one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Mann throws down dunk after steal

videos.description: Florida's Kevarrius Hayes emphatically rejects Braian Angola's shot attempt in the first half.
videos.headline: Hayes denies Angola's shot attempt

videos.description: After missing his initial shot attempt, Florida's Deaundrae Ballard grabs the offensive rebound and nails the layup.
videos.headline: Ballard grabs missed shot for second-chance points

videos.description: Florida State's Terance Mann draws the contact and coverts the layup for the 3-point opportunity.
videos.headline: Mann converts tough layup for and-1

videos.description: Florida State's Trent Forrest lobs a pass up to Terance Mann for the emphatic two-hand slam in the first half.
videos.headline: Mann hangs around on rim after alley-oop

videos.description: Florida State's Phil Cofer tries going up for a layup but is rejected by Florida's Keith Stone in the first half.
videos.headline: Stone denies Cofer

videos.description: Florida's Jalen Hudson breezes right past the Seminoles defense and earns a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Hudson goes coast to coast for and-1 chance

videos.description: Florida State's M.J. Walker leads Phil Cofer at the rim for the loud alley-oop slam late in the first half.
videos.headline: Cofer finishes one-handed oop

videos.description: After missing his initial shot attempt, Ike Obiagu grabs the offensive rebound and throws down the one-handed dunk in the paint.
videos.headline: Obiagu cleans up missed shot with the slam

videos.description: Florida's Jalen Hudson weaves through the Seminoles defense and knocks down the layup for a 3-point opportunity.
videos.headline: Hudson draws defenders in for and-1

videos.description: Florida State's CJ Walker draws in defenders with the jab step and nails the 3-point jumper.
videos.headline: Walker knocks down contested 3-ball

videos.description: Florida's Chris Chiozza lofts a pass up to Jalen Hudson at the rim for the loud alley-oop finish.
videos.headline: Chiozza finds Hudson above the rim for the oop

videos.description: Florida State's Terance Mann splits through the defense and finishes the crafty layup for a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Mann attacks the rim for and-1

videos.description: Terance Mann leads the Seminoles with 25 points in an 83-66 victory against the No. 5 Gators.
videos.headline: Florida State runs past Florida
